</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_324" id="161v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czü Plawen
